ction is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/78451/', '', 'Codeine, Oliceridine, Morphine, Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Meperidine, Butorphanol, Hydromorphone, Dezocine, Opium, Dextropropoxyphene, More', 'Ulipristal, Mifepristone, Ospemifene, Raloxifene, Bazedoxifene', 1767369485);
